description: Townhouse style 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home with 2 deeded parking spaces. Over 1,300 sq ft of living space on three levels. 1st floor is an open kitchen and living room with slider out to private rear deck. 2nd floor has two bedrooms with full bathroom. 3rd floor is primary suite. Large primary bedroom with ensuite full bathroom. Full basement offers laundry room and finished area suitable for home office or spare room. Located on the thriving West Side this property is very convenient to West Broadway and public transportation.Currently rented until 8/31/2025 Total current monthly rent is $4,800 Annual Rent $57,600 Monthly condo fee is $300. Showings by Appointment Only.
